  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b8e\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Enmar from Valvettithurai took refuge in Tamil Nadu",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "08 people from Jaffna's Valvettithura area have taken refuge in Tamil Nadu as refugees.",
        "Rameswaram Coast Guard rescued them and took them to the police station while they were going to Dhanushkodi area of \u200b\u200bTamil Nadu by boat from Valvettithurai.",
        "After investigations, arrangements will be made to accommodate them at the Mandapam refugee camp, the Coast Guard said.",
        "103 people have gone to Tamil Nadu as refugees from Sri Lanka since last March till today."
      ],
